	* mkdtemp.c [MINGW]: Include <io.h>.
	(mkdir): Define using _mkdir.

2006-06-28  Bruno Haible  <bruno@clisp.org>

	* wcwidth.h: Declare nothing if !HAVE_WCHAR_T. Provide a fallback
	declaration for wcwidth.
