	* fopen-safer.c: Merge minor changes from coreutils.
	* dup-safer.c: Likewise.
	* fd-safer.c: Likewise.

	Merge from coreutils.
	* stdio--.h: New file.
	* stdlib--.h: New file.
	* mkstemp-safer.c: New file.

	GNU tar needs these.
	* pipe-safer.c: New file.
	* creat-safer.c: New file.
