	* argp-help.c (canon_doc_option): Fixed coredump if *name==NULL
	(hol_entry_help): Never translate an empty string.
	Do not translate option tag (opt->name) if OPTION_NO_TRANS is set
	* argp.h (OPTION_NO_TRANS): New option.

