	Safer stack allocation.
	* setenv.c: Include allocsa.h.
	(alloca): Remove fallback definition.
	(freea): Remove macro.
	(__add_to_environ) [!_LIBC]: Use allocsa instead of alloca. Use freesa
	instead of freea.

