	* memcoll.c (STRCOLL): New macro.
	(memcoll): Use it.

2002-12-22  Bruno Haible  <bruno@clisp.org>

	* getstr.h (getstr): Define, to avoid clash with libcurses.
	* linebuffer.h (readline): Define, to avoid clash with libreadline.

